<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<odoo>
    <template id="globalgap_certification_application">
        <div>
            <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>PL-México: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.plmx"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>GGN: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.ggn"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Versión: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.globalgap_version"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Opción de Certificación: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.certification_option"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Tipo de Evaluación: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.evaluation_type"/></p></td>
                    
                </tr>
            </table>
            <h5 style="text-align:center;font-weight:Bold;">
                Addon
            </h5>
            <p>
                <t t-foreach="data.organization_id.addons_ids" t-as="addon">
                   <span>* </span><span t-field="addon.name"/>
                   <br/>
                </t>
            </p>
            <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="3" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:100%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Nombre de la Entidad Legal: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.name"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Dirección: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.address"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>CP: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.zip"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Ciudad: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.city_id"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Estado: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.state_id"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>País: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.country_id"/></p></td>
                    
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.email"/></p></td>
                    <td  style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.telephone"/></p></td>
                    
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>GLN: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.gln"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>RFC: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.vat"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="3" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:100%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Nombre CB: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.previous_cb"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Latitud: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.latitude"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Longitud: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.longitude"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Persona de contacto: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.contact_name"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Cargo: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.contact_position"/></p></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.contact_email"/></p></td>
                    <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                    <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="data.organization_id.contact_telephone"/></p></td>
                    </tr>
            </table>
            
            <p>
                <b>De acuerdo a los requisitos del documento de las Reglas de Acceso a Datos, 
                (que se adjunta y se localiza en www.globalgap.org/es/documents) indicar si:</b>
                <br/>
                <span t-field="data.organization_id.rights_of_access"/>
            </p>
            <div style="page-break-after: always;">
            </div>

            
            <t t-foreach="data.organization_id.production_site_ids" t-as="site">
                <h5 style="text-align:center;font-weight:Bold;">
                    INFORMACIÓN DE LOS SITIOS DE PRODUCCIÓN Y PHU
                </h5>
                <p>
                    <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                        <tr>
                        <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Nombre: </b><span t-field="site.name"/></p></td>
                            <td  style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Tipo: </b><span t-field="site.type"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Dirección: </b><span t-field="site.address"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>CP: </b><span t-field="site.zip"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Ciudad: </b><span t-field="site.city_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Estado: </b><span t-field="site.state_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>País: </b><span t-field="site.country_id"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="site.email"/></p></td>
                            <td  style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="site.telephone"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Latitud: </b><span t-field="site.latitude"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:50%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Longitud: </b><span t-field="site.longitude"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                    <h6 style="text-align:center;font-weight:Bold;">
                        Información de Contacto de <b><span t-field="site.name"/></b>
                    </h6>
                    <table style="width:100%; border:0px;">
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="3" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:100%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Persona de contacto: </b><span t-field="site.contact_name"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Dirección: </b><span t-field="site.contact_address"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>CP: </b><span t-field="site.contact_zip"/></p></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:40%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Ciudad: </b><span t-field="site.contact_city_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Estado: </b><span t-field="site.contact_state_id"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>País: </b><span t-field="site.contact_country_id"/></p></td>
                            
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="2" style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:70%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Email: </b><span t-field="site.contact_email"/></p></td>
                            <td style="border:0px; background-color:white; width:30%;">
                            <p style="text-align:left;"><b>Telefono: </b><span t-field="site.contact_telephone"/></p></td>
                            </tr>
                    </table>
                    <table style="width:100%; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px; color: black;">
                        <tr style="background-color: gray; color:white;">
                            <th style="width:40%;">Producto</th>
                            <th style="width:20%;">Hectáreas en producción (Sólo para Sitio de Producción)</th>
                            <th style="width:20%;">Para Certificar</th>
                            <th style="width:20%;">Producción Paralela (PP)/Propiedad Paralela (PO)</th>
                        </tr>
                        <t t-foreach="site.product_ids" t-as="product">
                            <tr>
                                <td><span t-field="product.product_id"/></td>
                                <td><span t-field="product.hectares_in_production"/></td>
                                <td><span t-field="product.to_certificate"/></td>
                                <td><span t-field="product.parallel_production_or_property"/></td>
                            </tr>
                        </t>
                    </table>
                    <!--<hr class="mt-0 mb-1" style="border-top: 1px solid"/>-->
                    <div style="page-break-after: always;">
                    </div>
                </p>
            </t>

            <p>
                <h5 style="text-align:center;font-weight:Bold;">
                    INFORMACIÓN DE PRODUCTOS
                </h5>
                <table style="width:100%; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 16px; color: black;">
                    <tr style="background-color: gray; color:white;">
                        <th style="width:10%;">Producto</th>
                        <th style="width:5%;">Área en producción (ha)</th>
                        <th style="width:5%;">Producción cubierta (Invernadero, Macrotúnel con cobertura plástica)</th>
                        <th style="width:5%;">Cosecha aplicable</th>
                        <th style="width:5%;">Primera Cosecha/ Cosecha Posterior</th>
                        <th style="width:5%;">Manipulación de Producto**</th>
                        <th style="width:10%;">Actividades Subcontratadas</th>
                        <th style="width:10%;">Si se subcontrata el empaque, indicar GGN o GLN (Obligatorio si tiene)</th>
                        <th style="width:5%;">¿El producto a auditar es manipulado con producto no certificado GLOBALG.A.P.?</th>
                        <th style="width:5%;">¿La organización compra el mismo producto certificado y/o no certificado?</th>
                        <th style="width:10%;">Rendimiento Estimado en Tons</th>
                        <th style="width:10%;">Fechas de cosecha estimadas</th>
                        <th style="width:15%;">Países</th>
                    </tr>
                   
                    <tr style="border:1px; border-color: black;" t-foreach="data.organization_id.product_information_ids" t-as="product_information">
                        <t t-set="countries" t-value="''"/>
                        <t t-foreach="product_information.countries_of_products" t-as="country">
                            <t t-set="countries" t-value="countries+country.name+' '"/>
                        </t>
                        <td style="border:1px; border-color: black;"><span t-field="product_information.product_id"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.uncovered_production_area"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.covered_production_area"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.applicable_harvest"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.harvest_type"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.product_handling"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.outsourced_activities"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.ggn_gln_outsourced"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.product_manipulated_not_certificate"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.organization_buys_product"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.estimated_yield_in_tons"/></td>
                        <td><span t-field="product_information.dates_harvest_estimated"/></td>
                        <td><t t-esc="countries"/></td>
                        
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </p>

        </div>
    </template>

</odoo>